&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;集群管理&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://gitee.com/dushixiang/kafka-map/raw/master/screenshot/clusters.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
